queries.sql: WITH RECURSIVE generation AS ( SELECT id_deputi, nama_deputi, parent_id, extention, 1 AS level_node FROM deputi WHERE parent_id =0 UNION ALL SELECT child.id_deputi, child.nama_deputi, child.parent_id, child.extention, level_node+1 AS level_node FROM deputi child JOIN generation g ON g.id_deputi = child.parent_id ) SELECT id_deputi,parent_id,nama_deputi,extention,level_node FROM generation order by parent_id asc;
